data.description: This 1930s home is very spacious, with high ceilings.  It has a large living room, and a large den. The kitchen has oak cabinets, and all kitchen appliances stay.  The living room has gas logs.  The bedrooms have beautiful hardwood floors.  There is a bonus room that could be a bedroom as well.  It has 2 bathrooms, with the washer and dryer being in one of the bathrooms.  The washer and dryer stays as well. It has a large yard, 0.52 acres.  Located close to everything.  House to be sold AS IS.  Great investment opportunity or a fixer upper.  The house does need some work.
